name: Fireal
additional_notices: The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en: FIREAL is an Asset Digitization Platform allows investors to manage, register, and invest in real-estate-backed NFT and dividend assets. They provide users with ecosystem FI-Share (Share To Earn), Fi-Shop (Shop To Earn) and Fi-Mining (Work To Earn) with a closed and flexible ecosystem, including investment, mining and staking.
